    {
      "scene_index": 7,
      "label": "第七场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四太监",
        "四官员",
        "大太监",
        "太监甲",
        "杨香武",
        "老王爷"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四太监引老王爷同上。大太监上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位先生，今乃老千岁寿诞，奉旨前来拜寿，你等可曾拜过咧？"
        },
        {
          "character": "四官员",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们恭候公公到来，一同拜寿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，这还等着我一同拜寿，拜过了大家吃杯寿酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老王爷",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳众公侯到来，又赠厚礼，焉敢受拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四官员",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "理当拜的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老王爷",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "实实不敢当。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，众位大人，倃们磕头，老千岁又不受，难道你我白来不成？咱们倒有一"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "番主意，请千岁就将圣上恩赐的四件东西，摆在上面，我们大家叩拜叩拜，犹"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如叩拜了王驾一般。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四官员",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有理。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四官员同声各坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四官员",
          "line_type": "同唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇王宣，各备寿仪，特来呈参。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "问问老千岁，今日不是有戏么，叫他们预备预备，倃们也听听。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四官员同宾白，同唱合前。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的人呢，将那九龙杯取来，咱家看看。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（大太监取。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位大人，你们来瞧瞧。这宗九龙玉杯，是当初日南交趾国进与当今万岁的，"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有许多的好处哩。咱们把寿酒斟在里头，大家喝他点儿，哎呀，多活十年。哈"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈，你们再看看，圣上赐的一轴图画，那是老王爷常常御览的，你们瞧瞧就知"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "道了。来，挂起它来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四官员同应。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四官员",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真正画得好！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四官员",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "眼似水铃鬃似针，尾长毛细都似真。配就山水多清雅，蹄跳咆哮似活龙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你赞的尽是骠满肥壮的马，咱家不喜，咱很爱这匹瘦小的马，倒有个看头儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四官员",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公公那匹马骨瘦如柴，要它何用？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱家当先也爱的是骠满的劣马，鞍鞯备好，乘跨起来，我就跑了马了么。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四官员",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公公爱跑马。如今呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如今有了年纪，所以这瘦马好，咱不能跑马，尽剩了收马咧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四官员 （同笑） 哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨香武暗上，偷杯，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天也是时候了。大家敬老千岁一玉杯寿酒，也好散席。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，快取九龙杯来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "太监甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启爷：九龙杯不见了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老王爷",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方才还在桌案上放著，怎生便不见了，好生奇怪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老王爷",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "九龙杯因何不见，"
        },
        {
          "character": "老王爷",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奇巧事令人憾然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老王爷",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "玉杯失去非等闲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老王爷",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "失杯怎去见天颜"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老千岁不必着紧，桌儿上桌儿以下，叫人细细找找罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四太监同找。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四太监",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寻找不着。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！我想这王府是禁地，难道有外人前来，再无此事。此府内外上下人等，不"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敢擅偷此杯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此事蹊跷难分辨，"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪有外人到此间。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱家倒想起来了，这件事总在老千岁身上所起。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四官员",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎见得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们不知道：前者老千岁在驾前奏道，洪海擒虎，是什么黄三泰，口称他是绿"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "林中的大盗。他既然是贼，应当将他拿住正法。倒赏了他件黄褂，这是自招其"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祸，定是作贼人贪心无厌，又来盗取玉杯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁爷，这是因行善事招出祸来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老王爷",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣上闻知失落此杯，那时怎生得了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但请放心，咱去奏明圣上，管保千岁无事。也不过奉旨到江南边，什么绍兴地"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方，把黄三泰拿进京来，这九龙杯就望他要定了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老王爷",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倘若不是他呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的老千岁爷，是他也得问他要，不是他也得问他要定了。不怕他不献出此杯"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老王爷",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此事全仗公公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老千岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我怎怠慢，"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明日五鼓面奏天颜。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（大太监、四官员同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老王爷",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武成过来，你如今外面密密访查，但有九龙杯的踪迹，急急前来禀我知道。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（武成应，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "老王爷",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慈心放虎去，反被虎伤人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老王爷下。杨香武上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨香武",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨香武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙吓，且喜九龙杯已到吾手，不免急到武成家中。单叫飞天豹，见见此物，方"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨香武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "显俺杨香武的手段。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（尾声） 双手破开生死路，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺也算绿林之中头，头一人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨香武下。）"
        }
      ],
